nce to strengthen the business landscape for Muslim-friendly products and services in Japan<ref name=\"HDC seals tie acrosx\"/>  .\n\n==References==\n{{reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Halal}}\n* [http://whc.hdcglobal.com/ World Halal Conference]\n* [http://knowledge.hdcglobal.com/ Halal Knowledge Centre]\n* [http://www.ghsc.com.my/ Global Halal Support Centre]\n* [http://www.halalpark.com.my// Halal Park by HDC]\n\n{{Federal Government of Malaysia}}\n\n[[Category:Government-owned companies of Malaysia]]\n[[Category:Ministry of International Trade and Industry (Malaysia)]]\n[[Category:Minister of Finance Incorporated (Malaysia)]]\n[[Category:2006 establishments in Malaysia]]\n[[Category:Companies established in 2006]]\n[[Category:Privately held companies of Malaysia]]\n", "name_user": "MB", "label": "safe", "comment": "Fix infobox image syntax", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Halal_Industry_Development_Corporation"}
